Setting Descriptions.invite: Server to join, leave as null without double quotes, if you do not want to join a server
Setting Descriptions.websocket: Should it establish a connection with the websocket after account generation (Helps not to get email / phone locked), disable if you just use to raid server real-time.
Setting Descriptions.hcaptcha_accessibility_token: Token for Captcha Bypass, get the hc-accessibility cookie @ https://www.hcaptcha.com/accessibility and put the content in the hcaptcha_accessibility_token property
Setting Descriptions.threads: Max concurrent registrations running at once. Actual threads are determined by your proxies speed / quality
